        "custom_background_color": false,
        "heading": "<h1>We Exist to Give Generously</h1>",
        "richtext": "<p>Our core value of generosity is at the heart of everything we do, from how we treat our employees, partners, vendors, and customers, to our affordable prices, warranties, and replacement policies.</p><p>We are also committed to giving away at least 10% of profits to various non-profit organizations, through a process that seeks input and contribution from every employee.</p>"
